# 🎯 Dotnet Playground

This project is a sandbox for learning and experimenting with **.NET Core** and a bunch of cool libraries and patterns.

---

## 🧪 Purpose

> Just playing around. No pressure, no production — only learning.

This project helps explore and understand:

- 🧱 ASP.NET Core fundamentals
- 🧩 Custom Mediator pattern (like MediatR)
- 🧮 Data access with **Dapper** and **NHibernate**
- 🗃️ Database migrations with **DbUp**
- 🧠 Architectural styles like Clean Architecture, CQRS, DDD

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack & Libraries

| Area              | Tool / Library      |
|-------------------|---------------------|
| Web Framework     | ASP.NET Core        |
| ORM               | NHibernate          |
| Micro ORM         | Dapper              |
| DB Migrations     | DbUp                |
| Mediator Pattern  | Custom Implementation |
| Error Handling    | ErrorOr             |
| DI & Configuration| Microsoft.Extensions |
| Extras            | FluentValidation

---

